---
title: Spicy Cajun-Inspired Tilapia with Lemon-Garlic Butter and Jewelled Rice
description: Who doesn't love good grilled fish?! We've decided to go the Cajun route and turn tilapia into a smoky, spicy delight! It finds its perfect home on jewelled rice filled with grilled peppers and zucchini. A finish of delectable lemon-garlic butter ensures this dish will be a hit!
